{"tid":853453,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得中學補習只係買一個心靈安慰","createTime":"2018-10-08T15:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T16:41:57.000Z","uid":77473,"like":77,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f41c6a22399bc457d06dbbb56755b81780aaf608","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"小學補習都叫有啲用<br />\n因為個個都唔溫書<br />\n係要有老師係度 咁先會專心溫<br />\n<br />\n但高中重補習真係好撚on9<br />\n有溫書的唔洗補 得閒返去搵下日校老師就得<br />\n冇溫書的補幾多 第二日都唔見左六成<br />\n<br />\n畀咁多錢去補習<br />\n只係想仔女大個左唔好埋怨當年老豆老母冇畀錢補習<br />\n搞到依家要打份牛工<br />\n利申:接過二十單私補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6982c0cb2d6387ffbc90918099a4835917b5e0fe","tid":853453,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa7bd1cdc3caaad42db662a6bff681ca83cb99ce","tid":853453,"uid":167330,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"認同，真係有心溫嘅自己溫都夠"},{"pid":"053d17f0d2d950f601a2f6433275021206ff7970","tid":853453,"uid":4876,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:18:41.000Z","msg":"你估個個日校老師都會理你咩<br />\n有啲人可能真係唔好彩撞正個教畜"},{"pid":"7b38b0d853cae32056f54e8dcc111e7e1311b565","tid":853453,"uid":119145,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"因為你唔稱職囉......<br />\n一個好補習老師<br />\n係應該幫個學生原本要1日溫既野，1個鐘就溫完"},{"pid":"d62cf3c6a604e163677a2de748684cb91900a02f","tid":853453,"uid":21460,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"我諗法相反...<br />\n小學嘢易，自己一定搞得掂，如果老母教畜管得好就無咩必要補習<br />\n中學有公開試，多咗啲鳩科(中文通識)，補習起碼畀到個方向你，就算get唔到方向都起碼有多啲source (e.g. mock, pp)<br />\n<br />\n利申對小學補習極反感，亦唔鼓吹中學補理科"},{"pid":"d2fe4337ea712b7b0519e19688c59a1d8274d0f8","tid":853453,"uid":71508,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n大把人補完入asso <br />\n例如補yy<br />\n大把人唔補都入asso<br />\n補習哂錢又哂時間<br />\n然後asso又升返大學<br />\n見返當年補習果啲中學同學/20幾分人<br />\n結論=唔需要補習。目標入asso就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c7f93d507314d119d7c7c7aec82d2f3c42d70c","tid":853453,"uid":135786,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e31bc0539ad41e475bd0f49d3b9e7e3249e3fb1","tid":853453,"uid":192776,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"唔係個個日校老師都有心幫學生溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n根本有好多老師都係冇料扮四條 以為自己做老師好撚高尚咁 對學生嘅態度差到仆街 教書嗰時又亂鳩咁嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對一啲學生嚟講唔補習靠自己同班濕鳩老師係好難先有好成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a938d93060a1a8d218ac4a18f2590af59644e2","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b38b0d853cae32056f54e8dcc111e7e1311b565","tid":853453,"uid":119145,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"因為你唔稱職囉......<br />\n一個好補習老師<br />\n係應該幫個學生原本要1日溫既野，1個鐘就溫完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"係一個鐘溫完<br />\n但死都唔溫書<br />\n過一排得返六成記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ."},{"pid":"44a04ba1b43ee633e24c9593502da6281c8951ac","tid":853453,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"有啲日校老師真係唔得㗎，無料或者唔識教，啲學生問多少少都話要返去搵資料然後不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n補習起碼你可以控制到係邊個教，學生成績同口碑係呃唔到人嘅，你唔鍾意嘅隨時可以走<br />\n至於補習狗值唔值個價就係另一個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於有無用就要睇同個學生夾唔夾得到<br />\n唔同人需要用唔同嘅教學方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ef2dc5966dba220ee5a86e47a085d5790fbb75","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:18:20.000Z","msg":"有時真係教得好氣餒<br />\n肯溫書的就有進步 <br />\n冇溫書就教幾多 即場係明係識<br />\n但幾個星期後就冇晒記憶<br />\n好似我的心血一嘢倒左落個無底洞度"},{"pid":"683179521aa903ef8928bfed533c80f344cd567d","tid":853453,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f41c6a22399bc457d06dbbb56755b81780aaf608","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"小學補習都叫有啲用<br />\n因為個個都唔溫書<br />\n係要有老師係度 咁先會專心溫<br />\n<br />\n但高中重補習真係好撚on9<br />\n有溫書的唔洗補 得閒返去搵下日校老師就得<br />\n冇溫書的補幾多 第二日都唔見左六成<br />\n<br />\n畀咁多錢去補習<br />\n只係想仔女大個左唔好埋怨當年老豆老母冇畀錢補習<br />\n搞到依家要打份牛工<br />\n利申:接過二十單私補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"點睇你師姐/妹做model?<br />\n<br />\n但樣衰"},{"pid":"e854bac3c9caf9c08cfbd3d7cca1fe49049717fc","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"683179521aa903ef8928bfed533c80f344cd567d","tid":853453,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f41c6a22399bc457d06dbbb56755b81780aaf608","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"小學補習都叫有啲用<br />\n因為個個都唔溫書<br />\n係要有老師係度 咁先會專心溫<br />\n<br />\n但高中重補習真係好撚on9<br />\n有溫書的唔洗補 得閒返去搵下日校老師就得<br />\n冇溫書的補幾多 第二日都唔見左六成<br />\n<br />\n畀咁多錢去補習<br />\n只係想仔女大個左唔好埋怨當年老豆老母冇畀錢補習<br />\n搞到依家要打份牛工<br />\n利申:接過二十單私補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"點睇你師姐/妹做model?<br />\n<br />\n但樣衰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"冇圖點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a33fa011dcab0a8ad58bd09115e8d4bc240eaf7","tid":853453,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a938d93060a1a8d218ac4a18f2590af59644e2","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b38b0d853cae32056f54e8dcc111e7e1311b565","tid":853453,"uid":119145,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"因為你唔稱職囉......<br />\n一個好補習老師<br />\n係應該幫個學生原本要1日溫既野，1個鐘就溫完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"係一個鐘溫完<br />\n但死都唔溫書<br />\n過一排得返六成記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"或者我講明d<br />\n即係個學生認真溫都要用1日 而你係要幫佢用1個鐘搞掂<br />\n如果個學生認真做都係1個鐘 咁你就唔稱職<br />\n即係你要令佢永遠都記得<br />\n咁先係一個好既補習老師 或者你冇遇過 所以冇體會"},{"pid":"a4bf81fe8b4407a91dd24aa1b0a007c48cdb8265","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a33fa011dcab0a8ad58bd09115e8d4bc240eaf7","tid":853453,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24a938d93060a1a8d218ac4a18f2590af59644e2","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b38b0d853cae32056f54e8dcc111e7e1311b565","tid":853453,"uid":119145,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:23:29.000Z","msg":"因為你唔稱職囉......<br />\n一個好補習老師<br />\n係應該幫個學生原本要1日溫既野，1個鐘就溫完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"係一個鐘溫完<br />\n但死都唔溫書<br />\n過一排得返六成記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:38:45.000Z","msg":"或者我講明d<br />\n即係個學生認真溫都要用1日 而你係要幫佢用1個鐘搞掂<br />\n如果個學生認真做都係1個鐘 咁你就唔稱職<br />\n即係你要令佢永遠都記得<br />\n咁先係一個好既補習老師 或者你冇遇過 所以冇體會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:47:08.000Z","msg":"一個鐘邊有可能有永遠記憶<br />\n你吹啦<br />\n<br />\n教我係有教 教埋佢點記 咁佢都要時間重溫 練下掛<br />\n講到補習就要補到佢立即曉飛咁<br />\n畀埋功課佢做(講緊半個鐘內一定做得晒 只係重覆我教過的嘢)<br />\n死都唔溫唔做 成五六次<br />\n問佢係唔係唔識做<br />\n我地依家重做晒<br />\n就私私然答太忙冇時間做(但我日日見佢ig出post去玩)<br />\n喱啲學生真係激死我<br />\n<br />\n重有啲成中六<br />\n永遠sba都死磨我<br />\n要我直接幫佢寫<br />\n我唔肯 話我地一齊寫中文 <br />\n佢自己返去組織做英文<br />\n結果又係一粒字都唔寫 直接十二點whatsapp我死磨話做唔切<br />\n好多嘢做 要我代寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睬佢都on9"},{"pid":"87e40297912c01c4a899e85e38a3b8eecdd6f6b1","tid":853453,"uid":209717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"高中補習其實好多係為資源，攞技巧<br />\n就咁講中文作文，出去補就已經多啲練習同範文啦<br />\n如果遇著個唔識教嘅日校老師，補習真心唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n但個啲補完唔溫唔睇，齋上堂，<br />\n當補習天王神咁拜，通宵排live個啲奇行種係on9"},{"pid":"24dbbcd2d4793dba37cc541cece66b5c5038e149","tid":853453,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e854bac3c9caf9c08cfbd3d7cca1fe49049717fc","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"683179521aa903ef8928bfed533c80f344cd567d","tid":853453,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f41c6a22399bc457d06dbbb56755b81780aaf608","tid":853453,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"小學補習都叫有啲用<br />\n因為個個都唔溫書<br />\n係要有老師係度 咁先會專心溫<br />\n<br />\n但高中重補習真係好撚on9<br />\n有溫書的唔洗補 得閒返去搵下日校老師就得<br />\n冇溫書的補幾多 第二日都唔見左六成<br />\n<br />\n畀咁多錢去補習<br />\n只係想仔女大個左唔好埋怨當年老豆老母冇畀錢補習<br />\n搞到依家要打份牛工<br />\n利申:接過二十單私補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:20:57.000Z","msg":"點睇你師姐/妹做model?<br />\n<br />\n但樣衰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"冇圖點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/005616_478472eb8f22695afdfc988dd9a5fcce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net